title: Scenes That American Horror Story Actors Regret Filming
author: Looper
comment: Who's your favorite actor from "American Horror Story"?

Genuinely think Dandy is the best acted character this show has ever had. Every actor wants to play the good guy/the hero, and I expect tons want to play the bad guy… but to play the foot stamping, whinging, mummy’s boy and play it so well… absolutely flawless acting from him.

Even Peters: "It's hard for me to play dark characters."
 Also Evan Peters: rushes to play Jeffrey Dahmer in another Ryan Murphy project

Everyone: Worrying and commenting about evan peters.
Gabourey Sidibe: Being scared that she offended papa legba
Oh my... Gabourey Sidibe's description of her experience is kinda chilling.
